$ Shell command: xmodmap
@ xmodmap

`xmodmap` displays and modifies the → hardware/keyboard modifier map and keymap table.

Using `xmodmap` is not recommended for complex tasks.

sa:

  → hardware/keyboard#keysym.

  → Linux/kernel/keymap

  → Linux/fhs/home/username/_xmodmaprc

  → Linux/shell/commands/index[Shell commands]
